1. On je dao *dušu* za svoju domovinu. (He gave his soul for his homeland.)
2. Ona je puna *duše* i nade. (She is full of soul and hope.)
3. Oni su potpuno izgubili *dušu*. (They have completely lost their soul.)
4. On je stavio *dušu* u svoj rad. (He put his soul into his work.)
5. Ona je unela *dušu* u ovu zgradu. (She brought soul into this building.)
6. Oni su prodali *dušu* za novac. (They sold their soul for money.)